00:29:35,900 --> 00:29:41,300
 Either you will hate one and love the other, or you will be devoted to one and despise

578
00:29:41,300 --> 00:29:42,740
 the other.

579
00:29:42,740 --> 00:29:46,980
 You cannot serve both God and money.

580
00:29:46,980 --> 00:29:48,780
 You will either be a servant of God."

