00:29:48,780 --> 00:29:49,780
 Even that's radical.

582
00:29:49,780 --> 00:29:50,780
 It's like, "Really?

583
00:29:50,780 --> 00:29:51,780
 I feel like I can.

584
00:29:51,780 --> 00:29:53,260
 God and the devil, maybe.

585
00:29:53,260 --> 00:29:54,260
 But God and money?

586
00:29:54,260 --> 00:29:55,820
 Can't we just prioritize them?"

587
00:29:55,820 --> 00:29:57,580
 And he says, "No, no, no.

588
00:29:57,580 --> 00:29:58,900
 You cannot serve them both.

589
00:29:58,900 --> 00:30:05,980
 You will either be a servant of God or you'll be a servant of money or a slave to money."

590
00:30:05,980 --> 00:30:06,980
 Which is it going to be?

591
00:30:06,980 --> 00:30:08,380
 You'll either serve one or serve the other.

592
00:30:08,380 --> 00:30:10,300
 You cannot have both.

593
00:30:10,300 --> 00:30:15,780
 Seeing who you serve and you really can see who you serve by how you spend.

594
00:30:15,780 --> 00:30:19,100
 Like how you use your money tells you, "Who am I a servant of?

595
00:30:19,100 --> 00:30:22,400
 How am I using this money?"

596
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:25,140
 Like in my registry, remember when I was registering?

