00:30:40,740 --> 00:30:41,740
 And you can't have both.

604
00:30:41,740 --> 00:30:43,020
 Jesus says, "You cannot serve.

605
00:30:43,020 --> 00:30:45,180
 You cannot be a servant of God and money.

606
00:30:45,180 --> 00:30:51,500
 Ultimately, you'll either serve God and you'll see money as something to use to serve him,

607
00:30:51,500 --> 00:30:52,500
 to serve the master.

608
00:30:52,500 --> 00:30:53,500
 It's his money.

609
00:30:53,500 --> 00:30:57,300
 I'm going to use it to serve him or you'll be a slave of money.

