00:31:02,020 --> 00:31:05,700
 But God says, "You cannot be neutral on this.

613
00:31:05,700 --> 00:31:08,940
 You cannot serve both money and me.

614
00:31:08,940 --> 00:31:14,460
 You're going to have to choose."

615
00:31:14,460 --> 00:31:19,520
 I think what's crazy about money is like you can move in the direction of serving money

616
00:31:19,520 --> 00:31:21,040
 without even realizing it.

