00:31:25,300 --> 00:31:26,620
 It owns you.

619
00:31:26,620 --> 00:31:30,700
 Like you've moving already in that direction where you're like, you no longer own it or

620
00:31:30,700 --> 00:31:32,400
 else you could decide what to do with it.

621
00:31:32,400 --> 00:31:33,400
 It owns you.

