00:31:56,100 --> 00:32:00,260
 And the first one that's a servant of God sees everything that they have, every dollar,

631
00:32:00,260 --> 00:32:05,400
 every moment, everything that they do as they are a steward of.

632
00:32:05,400 --> 00:32:06,400
 It's not theirs.

633
00:32:06,400 --> 00:32:07,400
 It's on loan.

634
00:32:07,400 --> 00:32:11,380
 The Bible teaches Psalm 24, "The earth is the Lord's and the fullness thereof."

635
00:32:11,380 --> 00:32:13,980
 Everything you have is right now on loan.

636
00:32:13,980 --> 00:32:16,720
 God says, "How are you going to steward it?"

