00:32:25,220 --> 00:32:26,860
 The owner says, "Do I have it in the bank?

642
00:32:26,860 --> 00:32:27,860
 Yeah, done.

643
00:32:27,860 --> 00:32:29,220
 Or I'll get a credit card and I'll buy it on credit."

644
00:32:29,220 --> 00:32:33,580
 A steward says, "God, would you have me buy this?"

