00:32:37,020 --> 00:32:39,460
 If there's a depression or recession, I want to have a nest egg.

647
00:32:39,460 --> 00:32:40,460
 I want to have backup.

648
00:32:40,460 --> 00:32:42,660
 I'm going to save as much as I can."

