00:33:05,740 --> 00:33:10,380
 And a steward says, "God, how much do you want me to keep?

659
00:33:10,380 --> 00:33:11,380
 It's all yours.

660
00:33:11,380 --> 00:33:15,500
 I want to be wise in the way that I steward it.

661
00:33:15,500 --> 00:33:19,580
 How do you see your money right now, everything that you have and I have?"

662
00:33:19,580 --> 00:33:20,580
 So convicting.

663
00:33:20,580 --> 00:33:24,880
 God says, "You are the steward of.

