00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:28,980
 You make a million dollars or you make $5,000.

665
00:33:28,980 --> 00:33:36,980
 You're going to give an account for how you stewarded every single penny, every dollar.

666
00:33:36,980 --> 00:33:45,020
 How do you see yourself, an owner or a steward, a servant of God or a servant of money?"

